{
  "stem": "4272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the Gestapo came and arrested me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at the time, they wouldn't tell me why.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took some smugglers that were in the village, and they took us all to this Starachowice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was using Wladyslawa Smiechowska.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at the time, I didn't have the papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tore them up in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To be with my sister, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't really have any papers at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they took me to prison in Starachowice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- and they interrogated me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a small room-- a very small room with a big desk and a big dog lying on the floor-- and they started to interrogate me in German because this man told them that I was teaching the Polish children, and that I was teaching them also German.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was afraid because it was enough one word, you know, spoken incorrectly, that I would pay with my life right away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said no, I only know a little German, what I was taught in school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And other than that, I would need a translator.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't understand you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, I understood everything what they were talking between them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were saying, should we play around any longer, or should we tell her why we arrested her?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Till finally they came out and they told me, you're Jewish, aren't you?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, that was after a while of me being in the village and being very much aware of what-- everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And occasionally of even going to church with the people from the village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I jumped up and I crossed myself and I said, I am Jewish?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How dare you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Who told you, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
